<subSubSection id="8E36CD77ED05D6803E4025A1707E4382" pageId="0" pageNumber="191" type="conditions of collecting">
<paragraph id="BAE5E93CB73A556F4041AD97DE763D11" pageId="0" pageNumber="191">Conditions of collecting.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A07A10657A032B5F925703698D276EA2" pageId="0" pageNumber="191">
Ten cases of 
<taxonomicName id="B660366137FD2EC0DC81D0E3EFD7E367" class="Insecta" genus="C." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="C. impalella" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="191" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="impalella">
<emphasis id="B03A3B9FF77E07232B69B1468D3AB77E" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="191">C. impalella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were collected in 
